MM look at the unpopular champions

{{champion:64}} {{champion:92}} {{champion:238}} {{champion:157}} {{champion:67}} {{champion:268}} {{champion:412}} 

People dislike being outplayed. They'd rather think it was just a matter of numbers so they can blame Riot. If another player beats them because they dodged their shit and pressed buttons correctly, it infuriates them. Because basically they cannot admit the other player played better. To the point where they will gladly disregard skill curve statistics and make up any excuse why they died to these champions.
